dream_text: I was soaring above the city skyline, feeling unburdened and free
interpretation: Flying dreams often symbolize liberation and ambition.

dream_text: I was falling endlessly from a skyscraper, and I felt terrified
interpretation: Falling dreams can reflect feelings of insecurity or fear of failure.

dream_text: I found myself swimming in calm waters under a starlit sky
interpretation: Water in dreams can represent deep emotions and the subconscious mind.
